---
title: American Kumara & Kidney Bean Enchiladas with Salsa & Chipotle Sauce
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Make a tasty bean filling, roll it up in soft flour wraps and then top the whole thing off with melted cheesy goodness. With a fresh salsa and dollop of plant-based sour cream, this vego meal is a real winner in our books.
